<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <h2 style="color: #c62828;">Account Deletion Request</h2>
    <p style="color: #555;">Use the OTP below to confirm your account deletion:</p>
    <div style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #c62828; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
      $otp
    </div>
    <p style="color: #555;">This OTP is valid for <strong>${validFor} seconds</strong>.</p>
    <p style="color: #e53935; font-size: 13px;">⚠️ This action is <strong>irreversible</strong>. Do NOT share this OTP with anyone.</p>
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 24px 0;" />
    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;">If you did not request account deletion, please contact support immediately.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

